parameters: There's a message from the headquarters...

I've checked on the auction matter. It seems that
human hunting is becoming more active in other
regions as well. There's no doubt that the auction
will be held in the near future. Now, as for the
crucial location, after gathering the
information...

We've narrowed it down to the fact that it will be
held in City A. I would like you guys to search in
City A as well. Other teams are also scheduled to
enter City A sequentially. That's all.

Also, I've provided some equipment, so please
check it.

※You've obtained the strongest equipment. If you
want to make battles easier, please equip it to
Esuka from the menu screen.

Is she... asleep? Maybe I should check the
computer...
I see, so A City is suspicious! Leave it to me!

The auction is held in secret, but of course, the
security should be tight. Please be careful.
Esuka is too rough with the machine...

It seems like it's going to take a while. Maybe I
should check the computer...

Alright, it's about time to finish the
maintenance.

This is our base. Although the Resistance has
several bases, this is one of them. Only a few
people within the Resistance know the location of
the headquarters.

Hmm! You've done something reckless again! The
machine is crying out! It needs immediate
maintenance!

This is Dr. Humbert. He's a collaborator with the
Resistance who defected from the Empire. He's also
the one who created Esuka's artificial body and
saved her life.

You're so noisy. If that's the case, then make it
more durable.
Esuka, you should rest for today at least.

Hmph! You know my body doesn't get tired like
this, right?

It's not a matter of the body, but of the heart.
You've been tense because of the auction recently,
haven't you? I'm worried about you.
...If Shuu says so, then I will...

Esuka has a younger sister she's been searching
for all this time. They were separated when they
fled from the Imperial Army as children, and she
hasn't been able to find any trace of her since
then.

Many people gather at the auction. There's a high
possibility that there could be a clue about her
sister there. It's no wonder that Esuka is
anxious.
I guess I should also get ready.
